        "text_C8fqKi": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><a href=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/septic-aid-septipods-6-pack\" title=\"https://environmentalbiotech.ca/products/septic-aid-septipods-6-pack\"><strong>Septic Aid™</strong></a> is designed to restore the natural bacterial balance in your septic system by introducing millions of powerful, beneficial bacteria. These bacteria support healthy microbial activity, helping to break down sludge and scum layers that can otherwise lead to backups or system failures.</p><p>Unlike ordinary septic treatments, Septic Aid™ offers a variety of easy-to-use application methods—including pourable liquids, flushable <em>Septipods</em>, and high-efficiency powered options—making it simple to choose the best fit for your home.</p><p>Every Septic Aid™ product is also formulated with built-in odor counteractants, delivering effective septic support while eliminating unpleasant smells from your home’s plumbing system.</p><h3><strong>Septic Aid™ Products for Home Use</strong></h3><p><strong>Septic Aid™ Liquid:</strong><br/><br/>Ideal for ongoing maintenance, just pour one capful weekly into kitchen sinks, bathroom drains, shower drains, or other household plumbing. This powerful liquid builds a protective biofilm to prevent clogs, hair buildup, soap residue, and odors—while also replenishing the beneficial bacteria your septic system depends on.</p><p><strong>Septic Aid™ Septipods:</strong><br/><br/>These water-soluble pouches offer a no-fuss solution—simply drop one in the toilet and flush. Perfect for homes with 2–4 bedrooms, Septipods help maintain a healthy bacterial balance and support long-term septic efficiency with minimal effort.</p><p><strong>Septic Aid™ Sachets:</strong><br/><br/>Similar in function to Septipods but designed for larger households (4+ bedrooms), Sachets deliver an extra boost of bacterial activity tailored to the demands of higher wastewater volume.</p><p>For optimal septic health, we recommend using <strong>Septic Aid™ Septipods or Sachets</strong> monthly as part of your regular home maintenance routine.</p>",
            "text_style": "body"
          }
        },
